  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Early access is expected to last approximately 60 minutes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/90d379e8e70a1b2d6e216743accc364e.avif?t=1745300932\" width=800 height=358 /></span>The newly renovated haunted house, <i>Hiyoshi Clinic</i>, was quickly becoming the centerpiece of Horizon Amusement Park. The protagonist, journalist Eiji Sakuma, visits the attraction for a report and finds himself immersed in a series of terrifying performances that seem far too real. Guided by a child's voice, he begins to experience strange phenomena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a haunted mansion set in a 1940s setting in FPS mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/e968d3e1e1b5025cc5afd45ea85dad79.avif?t=1745300932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras_big/e968d3e1e1b5025cc5afd45ea85dad79.avif?t=1745300932 width=800 height=436 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The eerie interior has been renovated while still retaining some of its original appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/a96ba99d42355e5c8d85bdab14fbe9fd.avif?t=1745300932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras_big/a96ba99d42355e5c8d85bdab14fbe9fd.avif?t=1745300932 width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inside the haunted mansion, there are puzzles and attractions to enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/3d29c55fdb6cfb3bd1ad1d6e99efa29a.avif?t=1745300932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras_big/3d29c55fdb6cfb3bd1ad1d6e99efa29a.avif?t=1745300932 width=800 height=478 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is also a collection element where you can collect the dolls placed inside the mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Early Access version is designed to offer approximately 60 minutes of gameplay, depending on how you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allows game commentary and broadcasting.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Early access is expected to last approximately 60 minutes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/90d379e8e70a1b2d6e216743accc364e.avif?t=1745300932\" width=800 height=358 /></span>The newly renovated haunted house, <i>Hiyoshi Clinic</i>, was quickly becoming the centerpiece of Horizon Amusement Park. The protagonist, journalist Eiji Sakuma, visits the attraction for a report and finds himself immersed in a series of terrifying performances that seem far too real. Guided by a child's voice, he begins to experience strange phenomena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a haunted mansion set in a 1940s setting in FPS mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/e968d3e1e1b5025cc5afd45ea85dad79.avif?t=1745300932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras_big/e968d3e1e1b5025cc5afd45ea85dad79.avif?t=1745300932 width=800 height=436 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The eerie interior has been renovated while still retaining some of its original appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/a96ba99d42355e5c8d85bdab14fbe9fd.avif?t=1745300932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras_big/a96ba99d42355e5c8d85bdab14fbe9fd.avif?t=1745300932 width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inside the haunted mansion, there are puzzles and attractions to enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras/3d29c55fdb6cfb3bd1ad1d6e99efa29a.avif?t=1745300932\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488790/extras_big/3d29c55fdb6cfb3bd1ad1d6e99efa29a.avif?t=1745300932 width=800 height=478 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is also a collection element where you can collect the dolls placed inside the mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Early Access version is designed to offer approximately 60 minutes of gameplay, depending on how you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allows game commentary and broadcasting.</p>",
